This paper deals with image repurposing detection, which is a problem related to computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the use of adversarial learning, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves the detection of semantic manipulation, which is a problem in information retrieval (cs.IR) and cybersecurity (cs.CR). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.MM, followed by cs.CR, cs.IR, and cs.LG.
